00:24:18.205 --> 00:24:24.185
She was also sold to the English by the Bugundians, inhabitants of modern France, although

00:24:24.285 --> 00:24:28.845
it’s debatable whether they would have referred to themselves back then as French.

00:24:30.175 --> 00:24:34.445
And finally, she was betrayed, or at least not saved,

00:24:34.715 --> 00:24:37.905
by none other than the French king, Charles VII.

00:24:38.625 --> 00:24:44.325
He had the chance to save her from the flames, yet he did absolutely nothing.

00:24:45.492 --> 00:24:49.342
So, she might be a French heroine, but she wasn't treated

00:24:49.342 --> 00:24:52.322
so well by her fellow citizens when she was alive.

